		DIVERSIFIED ASSETS AND SKILLED PROFESSIONALS

		Ontario Teachers' is a global investor and one of the world's leading pension plans. Recognized for our history of performance, we invest responsibly on behalf of our members. We strive to be agile and innovative while developing strategies and building partnerships for the long term.
















